::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod continued to keep cover, and fire on the CFs attackers.

::DrillBit::

DrillBit stayed near the caves mouth, shooting at the Maximals.

::K9::

K9 took the crystal, and started walking out.
"I dont know what these attacks are about. I just joined the war. I
picked up a battle, and responded. Now I'll get this to that bot,
Kluster." He walked out of the ship, and started running to the CF.
